      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/nie/2025/09/25/6TEWJLWCOJDWLMDJFDWIQYPVPI/</guid>
      <dc:creator>유석재 역사문화전문기자, 기획·구성=윤상진 기자</dc:creator>
